== Overview ==
The Vidian Industries Shield Displacer uses a new technology to set it above and beyond the performance of the standard [[:Category:Weapons (Shield Disruptors)|shield disruptor]] series.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Shield Displacer can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
